name: COMMONWEALTH Of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. David HOLLOWAY, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of September, 2012, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 80 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
